{"tid":262747,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【贏家係佢】李嘉誠與AlphaGo之父會面：參與早期投資是緣分","createTime":"2017-05-29T12:47:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-30T05:01:11.000Z","uid":30561,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dfdb3fdfe2bd31e9f9c6d3578c917e1125b6a51c","tid":262747,"uid":30561,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T12:47:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/pic/0/10/11/67/10116754_834579.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fpic%2F0%2F10%2F11%2F67%2F10116754_834579.jpg&h=7172fbac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【橙訊】由DeepMind創辦的AlphaGo剛剛在內地擊敗了「中國棋王」柯潔，再次引起全世界的關注。不過，你是否知道原來香港首富李嘉誠是DeepMind最早的投資者之一，DeepMind的兩位創辦人在上周五就來到香港，與李嘉誠見面。<br />\n<br />\n據李嘉誠基金會的官方微博在今日中午左右出貼文，寫道：「李先生上週五一早準備好「紙筆墨」，因為DeepMind兩創辦人Demis和Mustafa到香港為他「上課」，講解人工智能研究方向與各種應用的階段成果，李先生要摘錄筆記。Demis對政府政策如何支持和平衡人工智能的發展有自己的洞見&mdash;對用於國防和武器發展不無顧慮；李先生聽課很激動，數度站起來，害得兩創辦人也連忙禮貌地陪站。李先生覺得能參與DeepMind早期投資是可貴的緣份。」<br />\n<br />\n實際上，DeepMind在2011年創辦。在2014年，Google斥資約31.2億港元收購這家英國的人工智能公司，但其實，在Google投資之前，李嘉誠便已經投資了DeepMind，成為其最早的股東之一。<br />\n<br />\n關於投資DeepMind，李嘉誠知道在2016年3月舉辦的年度業績記者會上才第一次透露，當時正值AlphaGo戰勝韓國棋王李世石，李嘉誠當時在記者會上分享了對AlphaGo的想法，他說，「第一要恭喜Google，第二他很欣賞李世石，那種風度，那種毅力，是值得欽佩的。雖然我不下圍棋，但我知道它的道理。」<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/pic/0/10/11/67/10116755_914480.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fpic%2F0%2F10%2F11%2F67%2F10116755_914480.jpg&h=d610d89a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對於投資的回報，李嘉誠只是承認，「在AlphaGo之前有投資，賺了錢，賺了好多倍。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">這麼一說，其實誠哥是不是才是AlphaGo的最大贏家？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/finance/system/2017/05/28/010059177.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Ffinance%2Fsystem%2F2017%2F05%2F28%2F010059177.shtml&d=5kcKS88VDqQHtVy1SgIa4f6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=ea7e5443\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.orangenews.hk/finance/system/2017/05/28/010059177.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">李嘉誠上人工智能課激動站起</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/262739/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/262739/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"8143d2c18550afaa28456fb973276bbe3e929761","tid":262747,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T13:02:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"950007bdc92f2af30217c1630d4d1255ec793ec1","tid":262747,"uid":19654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T13:13:49.000Z","msg":"誠哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e266f450927fc9c6238b4bfb07d9e74feb3967e","tid":262747,"uid":38465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T13:16:22.000Z","msg":"誠哥既眼光真係好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bc8d4301ccc9e07ffde41ca3951c3f91a8c42d1","tid":262747,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T13:17:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dee7d5f4f2ffe076b45c05a24723027fe3422139","tid":262747,"uid":12458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T13:17:48.000Z","msg":"誠哥咁有錢都醫唔好駝背 陰公！"},{"pid":"849e03aae05f05c547d586682c76c14bbdec1989","tid":262747,"uid":19654,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T13:18:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好小老一輩既人唔識玩圍棋<br />\n<br />\n佢後生個陣鐘意玩乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n玩鳩香港人"},{"pid":"a9ea69e7b8ce2edc68aaa1afea8be2eeb979fd82","tid":262747,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T13:18:45.000Z","msg":"誠仔好似後生左"},{"pid":"4b91aa6d53d33bc0f40ae61d0d66ed640421551d","tid":262747,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply